snippet.title: The beginning｜Mad World - Age of Darkness - MMORPG｜Official Announcement Trailer
snippet.description:
Mad World Official Launch on April 27th (Thur)
✨Pre-registrators: https://www.madworldmmo.com

The peaceful sky of Gruzaam was ripped open by the Abyssal Sky, through which demon invasion began.
Countless people stood together to protect their families and beloved ones against the demons.
Alas, humans met gruesome defeat in their battle, and now Gruzaam is dominated by demons.
And now begins the story of Shadow Children that survived the massive massacre.

The legend of Mad World begins…
=====================================
The number of pre-registrators already reached 100 thousand!
Now let us aim for 300 thousand!

If you didn't take part in the pre-registration event yet, now is your chance!

✨Pre-registrators: https://www.madworldmmo.com
=====================================
✨MadWorld official site
👉Discord: https://discord.gg/madworldmmo
👉Homepage: https://www.madworldmmo.com
